name: Super Australia Man
description:
The Australian wildlife is out for blood!

Try to survive the hordes of animals for as long as possible in this fast paced arcade boomerang-bending (?) game!

Features:

  1. Innovative gameplay!
  2. 6 unique enemies to fight!
  3. Randomly generated levels! 
  4. Complex score mechanics that reward skill!
  5. Cool Voxel art graphics!
  6. Janky animations!
  7. M&K and controller support!
  8. Plenty of options!
  9. Dynamic music!
